{"tid":890854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"豆腐花爭霸戰","createTime":"2018-11-05T15:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T16:20:09.000Z","uid":187102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c16fa46319ca34d59aa822c75f832f7052bb332e","tid":890854,"uid":187102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"頭先荃灣路德圍諗住食下野<br />\n見到好多人排隊買豆腐花<br />\n原來做緊$2優惠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ozdYaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ozdYaQ.png&h=eb51fbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申非打手<br />\n平常兩間都有食<br />\n見佢寫住應對方法 豆腐花兩蚊<br />\n姐係有人對付佢啦 <br />\n咁人地本身點對付佢呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4iY9h8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4iY9h8.png&h=ea90da5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來有人想用三蚊豆腐花攻擊人<br />\n咁既然你不仁 就唔好怪人我不義啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcWTdLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcWTdLq.png&h=5dabdd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔離直接收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs綠色個間個人覺得有啲仆街<br />\n記得之前新年佢趁黃色冇開檔<br />\n佢將啲豆腐花加撚到廿幾蚊碗<br />\n隔離開番又變五蚊<br />\n<br />\n仲有綠色唔同地方原來唔同價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4733f1a244e7515711e7adc651a66c026332377b","tid":890854,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"應該就快打架 不過有利消費者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859cdb381aa859c5682075fb5db2f81b9a06f0e6","tid":890854,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"🥜"},{"pid":"3253178fda875a6992f30a5c6d5467ca4fb84717","tid":890854,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"屌鳩綠色就唔好遮名"}]}